## Tone Guidelines

### Do's
- Use clear, concise language
- Write in [first/second/third] person
- Use active voice
- Keep sentences [short/medium/varied]
- Include [emojis/no emojis] in casual contexts

### Don'ts
- Avoid jargon unless industry-standard
- Don't use overly formal language
- Avoid negative framing
- Don't make claims without evidence

